            <h3>The Backstory</h3>
            <p>Yo! We are Bort and Caleb...and we’re excited that you’re checking out this project. At one point along this path, we were both simply concerned about getting easier access to fresh herbs to cook with. Immediately, we noticed a bump in flavor and freshness from our homegrown herbs. We also began to realize that growing your own herbs has other perks: convenience, less waste, and saving some serious dough at the grocery store (especially if you already opt for organic). </p>
            <p>We also found fulfillment in learning how to keep plants alive...err...how to cultivate our own personalized collection of fine herbs! We found a creative outlet in selecting plants that complemented our favorite cooking styles and cocktail recipes. It evokes a honest sense of pride and badassery when you walk out your back door, snip off a couple sprigs of flat-leaf parsley, and use that astounding aroma and flavor to bring out the highest potential in your own inspired culinary creation. We are home cooks, cocktail enthusiasts, native Washingtonians, and big fans of living the Good Life…join us on that journey!</p>
