            <h3>Bort</h3>
            <p>It started as most great adventures do - with a stiff drink. I believe it was a "South Side". See, when I set out to refine my cocktail crafting capabilities, I quickly realized two things. First, drinks made with fresh herbs are the sh*t. Second, it's expensive and super wasteful to buy those herbs at the store. The solution was obvious, and what started as a few plants on a window sill has grown into a full-fledged passion project.</p>
            <p>I love building things and I love sharing my interests with others. Be it a piece of software or a plant installation, I find immense joy in taking a concept and shaping it into a reality. I believe life is short, and it should be spent eating the best food, drinking the best drinks, and generally enjoying the best that this green earth has to offer.</p>
